<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Withdrawal Successful</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: -20px -20px 30px -20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 20px 20px 20px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .transaction-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f5576c;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f5576c;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .details .row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .details .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
        .details .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="status-icon">üí∏</div>
            <h1>Withdrawal Successful!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>

            <div class="transaction-box">
                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0;">Your withdrawal has been processed successfully</p>
            </div>

            <div class="amount">
                {{amount}} RWF
            </div>

            <h3>Transaction Details</h3>
            <div class="details">
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Transaction Reference:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{transactionReference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Account Number:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{accountNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Previous Balance:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{balanceBefore}} RWF</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">New Balance:</span>
                    <span class="value"><strong>{{balanceAfter}} RWF</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Date & Time:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{timestamp}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> If you did not authorize this withdrawal, please contact our support team immediately.
            </p>

            <p>Thank you for banking with Credit Jambo.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Credit Jambo Ltd</strong></p>
            <p>For assistance, contact our 24/7 support center.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
